CONTEXT CompositionTypeCheck IN ENGLISH

PURPOSE CONTEXT CompositionTypeCheck
{+ Test that composition succeeds when target of left operand matches source of right operand.
   This verifies the type checker correctly accepts r[A*B];s[B*C] yielding [A*C]. +}

RELATION r[A*B]
RELATION s[B*C]
RELATION result[A*C]

RULE testComposition: result = r;s

ENDCONTEXT
